reviews.title: Works when it feels like it.
reviews.comment: You guys are great as a banking institution, but this app is quite a joke unfortunately. Majority of the time, it would just quit/giving up & showing errors, making retrieving my account information a nuisance. Please care for your clients and build a more respectable application e.g Chase Mobile or the like. Thanks.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: MUCH improved
reviews.comment: This app was terrible up until the latest update. The UI was completely overhauled and went from an outdated mess to a functional experience. I\'ve had no trouble logging in and the new look is nice. Good job devs.
reviews.author: Sam H

reviews.title: The update was well needed.
reviews.comment: The app before worked just enough to function. I had many of the issues people have mentioned before, the most crippling was the white screen bug. It was so bad that I had better results on the mobile website, but all of that is gone now on my Note II. It finally looks decent and it functions much more smoothly and quickly. Now, if there was a way to integrate savings goals and reports into the app and make it more useful, more so than functional it would deserve five stars. For my troubles, ill give it 3.

reviews.title: Awesome

reviews.title: Sooo much better
reviews.comment: This is update makes the app so much nicer and easier to use. Make it a little bit more smooth and it\'d be perfect! A swipe to the right gesture to open the menu and a removal of the fifty cent mobile deposit fee would be great as well, but that\'s just nitpicking. Thank you!

reviews.title: Better but still issues
reviews.comment: Check deposit problems continue. Kind of annoying. It does not allow me to deposit checks consistently because \"the amount entered does not equal the amount detected.\" Obviously the app is not detecting the correct amount.

reviews.title: Worthy of use
reviews.comment: A app that is now worthy of use. No longer is the app more of a shortcut to the site but its a actual app. Like that checks can now be deposited with app just think it should be free. this was a much needed option as other banks already allowed. Do wish I knew last week when I was out of state in Washington state as I only made it to a branch because I drove by one & did not know I would be near one. I was glad because I did not want to carry such a large check for a long time with no good way to secure it.
